# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [0.3.0] - 2015-12-30
### Added
- customization for links and success buttob
### Changed
- Updates icon glyphs. Added start-o, circle-o-dotted, redo icons
- SearchSelect: Pass value to `this.props.onChange` as a second argument.
### Fixed
- Really close tooltip  if it received trigger="close" prop
- In SearchSelect shown results even for empty pattern
- Border radius in tooltip
- Datepicker: handle incorrect value

## [0.2.0] - 2015-12-13
### Added
- icons font in woff2-format
- Spinner component
- ScrollContainer component
- Loader component

### Changed
- Updates icon glyphs. Added vacation and sick icons
- SearchSelect has select = -1 in initial state
- Added height of input (small, default, large)
- Added toooltip trigger options (opened, closed)
- Dropped react 0.13 support
- Passed autoFocus prop to Input and Textarea
- Added mask prop to Input

### Fixed
- pointer cursor for checkbox
- vertical-align fot DatePicker and Group

## [0.1.0] - 2015-10-22
First version